So, one of my friends has recently got back into Magic because of MTGA. Obviously I tell him about commander and he seems interested. He loves New Phyrexia as it was his introduction to Magic.

He tells me he wants to play Vorinclex as his commander, and worried about MonoGreen as limiting. I tell him about the hate it would generate and he drops this gem on me:

“I think that Commander should be about reaping as much schadenfreude as possible instead of trying to win.”
So...mono green stax it is.
